Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  早上…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸頭小子來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在簽約的話您就一定能獲得情侶溫泉旅行券
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣  很划算吧  很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和先生一起偶爾去放鬆下筋骨如何  夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫  夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來給您擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啊  裕理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沒有別人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕理…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢  溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:04:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧  那麼就趕緊在這份莫名其妙的契約書上簽名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在打壞主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？  當然是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵺！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢  白獸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類可是騙子成群的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共存的第一步就是相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不先好好談談的話怎麼知道是真還是假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個天真的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬讓我拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去還給八衢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底八衢也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬要是動真格的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕車旅行還真是開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經有真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…只有我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人不知道  但裕…裕理先生  怎…怎麼會發生那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是夫婦夫婦  真奇怪到現在都還沒有共寢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼你會知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…以為我沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是新聞機構已經開始關注了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從決定要幫助你們那時起  就做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報控制和相關各部門的聯動就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  亞芽裏已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全恢復到平時狀態了  放學後還說要去卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬小姐如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  Flawless禁止去那樣的地方麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有去過…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有去過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  白白也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  什麼事都要經歷一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我跑去打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是希望能和你…做朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不嫌棄的話我十分樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  那麼放學後車站前見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是共存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹啥  突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友  共存存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友  共存存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友朋友  共存存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友朋友  共存存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹啥幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友朋友  共存存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個月的新歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張著的美冬也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣播中流淌的旋律  是否引起你的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時這顆心靈僅以石頭自擬  在閉合的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找尋已久的櫻桃樹前  如今可還有你在身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清晨灑遍滿地晶瑩的朝露  誰也阻止不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一起去買東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一個是白白哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  總是和機械不太投緣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種事習慣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得很幸福的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在想什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有看得入神…真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得能和裕理先生相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才和亞芽裏小姐還有大家都成為了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又接近綺久羅美的理想一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  請快點起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到和亞芽裏小姐她們約好的時間前還能再出一把汗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  才剛起床…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  失敗失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早還早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了三強以外太轉依的總數有數萬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數…數萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是居然被折磨成這德行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  只是輕微做點修煉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用連這種日子都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  不要啄那種地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是由美奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然和鳳凰相處得如此親密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是共存的具現化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能毫不在乎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美奈由美奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看著哥哥他們而已  只是那樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady記得來不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕理  能去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紅白相間的建築物是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好嗎  比這好玩的地方多的是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想爬上去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的東西居然出自人類之手  簡直是驚天動地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕理先生  抱歉這麼任性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  今天本來就是打算陪真白才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就交給亞芽裏大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  太傳統了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個當作白白和裕的情侶裝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不穿！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}偉人  怪人大集合！！塔內名產  蠟人像館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該這樣…  靠過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那邊笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想都沒想過要肉和蔬菜這樣夾在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白  嘴角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒樣子  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕理先生也撒出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自…自己來就行了  好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  這個看起來也挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從剛才就一直在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒察覺到你們也太大意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  那邊的小夫妻  笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  已經有孩子了嗎  真是精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩  孩子…  我和裕理先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情還…  才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哈呀  真是羨煞旁人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵  拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從這裏一邊看外面一邊上去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過用飛的不是更快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這樣也有這樣的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本升降機正前往離地高150公尺的大瞭望台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到外面了外面  外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  外面  是外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高呢  不過很讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠嗆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到下面了  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞芽裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個啊…  裕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社是在那邊吧  裕理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  我還以為是這邊一直在看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白不睏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次  下次想兩人個單獨出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了  綺久羅美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸頭爆炸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸頭啊  爆炸頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸頭爆炸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸頭  爆炸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面是爆炸頭  下面也是爆炸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是爆炸頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…

